To complete the analysis and confirm that CAS is indeed struggling, I want to compare the total amount spent by each college throughout the years on their
employees. This is easily done in a query below:

SELECT SUM(DISTINCT `Base Pay`), College, Year
FROM salaries_final
GROUP BY College, Year


In the chart, you can see that in 2009, money allocated to CAS was higher, but by 2020 COM overtakes it. Furthermore, according to an article, CAS
already has a shortfall of 27 million for the year 2020. This indicates that not only --
